\begin_layout Paragraph
How do I get a ride or offer a ride? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
When you register for a event, the REGI system will ask whether you can
 offer others a ride or if you need a ride yourself.
 Once you are approved for the event, you will be able to see other participants
' carpooling information.
 Who is coming, where they are coming from, whether they are offering or
 requesting rides, and their email address.
 You can then email them and offer to carpool with them.
 
\end_layout

