\begin_layout Paragraph
What do I do if I’m WAITLISTED? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
If there the event is currently full, the leader will place you on a waitlist
 and you will receive an automated email from the system letting you know
 that your registration status has been updated to 
\emph on
WAITLIST
\emph default
.
 If spots open up on the event, the leader will contact you to offer you
 a spot.
 If you are taken off the waitlist, your registration status will switch
 to “APPROVED” and you will receive an automated email to this effect.
\end_layout

